            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "So what would $30K in 1987, and a now $275K get you in 2021 from the GNX? A whole lotta car, even in stock form. Clearly, what set this ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
